Skypay Banking System

ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

Skypay is a simple banking system that allows users to manage their bank accounts by performing operations such as depositing, withdrawing, and viewing their transaction history. The system follows an Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) approach with Java and uses Lombok for reducing boilerplate code.

